\title{Biographical info ([Sellars](sellars))}

\p{Roywood Sellars was his father, a successful philosopher.}
\p{Undergrad philosophy in Michigan working with his father. MA working on [Husserl](husserl)'s phenomenology (you can see his father's critical realism showing strongly in that thesis). He was a wrestler and a fencer. Failed to write a [Kant](kant) dissertation at Oxford, came to Harvard to work with [Quine](quine).
}
\p{Sellars had spent 10 years in academia without publishing anything.}

